{"tid":1135124,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"做工苦，難道不做工就不苦嗎？","createTime":"2019-05-02T06:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T06:51:10.000Z","uid":120123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e03a6518c9e197d2df5b94ca26d76bbb1d812055","tid":1135124,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:18:38.000Z","msg":"要幾撚弱智同on9先講得出呢句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"53588397c6352875c18147970cb8073c44fe8c91","tid":1135124,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:20:55.000Z","msg":"我相信李十X真心享受工作"},{"pid":"55ce76adc6b427a3457f21abee5a354aeef3f477","tid":1135124,"uid":120123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:21:28.000Z","msg":"人生從出胎的那一秒鐘起到絕氣的那一秒鐘止，除了睡覺以外，總不能把四肢、五官都擱起不用。只要一用，不是淘神，便是費力，勞苦總是免不掉的。會打算盤的人，只有從勞苦中找出快樂<br />\n<br />\n以前d人奴性真係好撚勁，自己做奴隸被奴役，重要從勞苦中找出快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04ac68d9dae16d085df95e645f1d1d06b270188","tid":1135124,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:22:52.000Z","msg":"第二等苦人，便是厭惡自己本業的人，這件事分明不能不做，卻滿肚子裡不願意做。不願意做逃得了嗎？到底不能。結果還是皺著眉頭，哭喪著臉去做。這不是專門自己替自己開玩笑嗎？&emsp;<br />\n<br />\n係呀，被人老強你都逃避唔到架，開開心心被老強啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n不願意被老強逃得了嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5fecd5c86085accba4a5550d5315d8ab2c9fd4","tid":1135124,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:23:41.000Z","msg":"咁你想點 唔係二世祖就唯有勤力啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec293891f48427ff5f8ef31660af87ff49295f9","tid":1135124,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:24:07.000Z","msg":"結論：樓主返下賤工雞碎咁多人工，好撚痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f2031bcb089b7649f46b5d272b76613a10d5ff","tid":1135124,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:24:27.000Z","msg":"凡做一件事，便把這件事看作我的生命，無論別的什麼好處，到底不肯犧牲我現做的事來和他交換。我信得過我當木匠的做成一張好桌子，和你們當政治家的建設成一個共和國家同一價值；我信得過我當挑糞的把馬桶收拾得乾淨，和你們當軍人的打勝一支壓境的敵軍同一價值。大家同是替社會做事，你不必羨慕我，我不必羨慕你。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"5f17fcbb1248481778a3d992ed5373a4fa8f7288","tid":1135124,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:26:16.000Z","msg":"究竟以前cert level 教書班友有幾撚痴線先會將呢篇野列做範文？<br />\n以前讀書果陣唔覺有野，出來做野真係覺得呢篇野痴孖根。<br />\n完全係廢老打飛機文章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408e344c17f1662dc980fa83b263d8ff2496b24f","tid":1135124,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:35:17.000Z","msg":"邊條on9仔講架<img src=\"/assets/fa